    <accessrestrict encodinganalog="506">
      <head>Access Restrictions</head>
		 <p>The majority of our archival and manuscript collections are housed offsite and require advanced notice for retrieval. Researchers are encouraged to contact us in advance concerning the collection material they wish to access for their research.</p>
      <p>Originals of two of the three scrapbooks are restricted due to fragile condition and may not be opened without special permission.  Photocopies are provided in the collection.  Access to beta tapes requires advance notice to produce working copy.</p>
    </accessrestrict>
